{"tid":490680,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"［豬扒食家］樂仔生涯拍過詩詠巧音伊汶雨雯，結婚終於遇到女神","createTime":"2017-12-05T23:58:16.000Z","updateTime":"2017-12-06T10:09:22.000Z","uid":41351,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"daf66fff9666170cf30917ee1696b039e2e1cf0d","tid":490680,"uid":41351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-05T23:58:16.000Z","msg":"余文樂與公開戀情近一年的女友王棠云（Sarah）結婚，今日在IG上載結婚照，與大家分享新婚的喜悅心情。其實樂仔過往與多位圈中人拍拖，包括當年拍攝港台劇集《青春@Y2K》時，曾跟唐詩詠拍拖，分手後遇上盧巧音，可惜這段「姊弟戀」並未被外間看好，分手後再搭上黃伊汶及吳雨霏，仍未能開花結果。<br />\n<br />\n直至去年12月，樂仔終於在網上承認與28歲台灣藝人王棠云（Sarah）拍拖，Sarah爸爸王東生有「皮帶大王」之稱，她可算是富二代。樂仔與Sarah亦愛得癡纏，不時上載拍拖照。<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/075756_9cac465671d75d34d86d1df945474675.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F075756_9cac465671d75d34d86d1df945474675.jpg&h=ffc3a3de&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/075756_37b27e607de0230db82117117fd58190.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F075756_37b27e607de0230db82117117fd58190.jpg&h=1f7bbd9c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/075758_e1449808576a7f8158dad0a4ba1dc2fd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F075758_e1449808576a7f8158dad0a4ba1dc2fd.jpg&h=0a5f66e4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/075800_92e01b94d7cea0e4f378af64562dc468.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F06%2F075800_92e01b94d7cea0e4f378af64562dc468.jpg&h=f5f772cc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"01b97cb40628ccc36e41fc548336661f3faab2d2","tid":490680,"uid":41351,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-06T00:00:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/06/075939_bcde